    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Ferenc Thurzó and Hungarian Chamber (Vienna, 23
                    November 1551)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">1. The censura that the Chamber sent in connection with
                            István Dobó’s administration did not take into consideration what Oláh
                            had already tried to make them understand before. Oláh has therefore
                            stayed here in Vienna and did not follow the King, and he spent three
                            days working on revising the censura and wrote a mitigation that follows
                            the articuli to accompany it. He has sent it to them so they can see why
                            he may have been lenient with Dobó. 2. He asks them to read his
                            mitigation as soon as possible and decide in the case while the King
                            returns to Vienna; royal constrascriba Péter Gutai will help them with
                            it. He has also written to Dobó to prepare and send the annual
                            accounting for the year 1551. György Kachich will tell them the rest. 3.
                            They should inform Oláh about their intentions as soon as possible, so
                            he can find a suitable inspector. Although he is sending this letter to
                            Ferenc Thurzó as well, he has heard that he has not returned to
                            Bratislava yet, so they should decide without him. </p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Reverendi ac Egregii Domini, Fratres et Amici Honorandi, salutem et
                    nostri <choice>
                        <orig>co<gap extent="1" reason="damage" unit="word"/>ndation<gap extent="1"
                                reason="damage" unit="word"/></orig>
                        <supplied>co<corr>mme</corr>ndation<corr>em</corr></supplied>
                    </choice>!</p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">[1.] Censuram, quam superioribus temporibus Dominationes Vestrae
                    super administratione <persName>Stephani Dobo</persName><note xml:id="note.1"
                        >István Dobó.</note> ad nos miserant, quamvis prius cognoscere atque nostram
                    superinde opinionem Dominationibus Vestris describere voluerimus, praesentia
                    tamen <persName>maiestatis regiae</persName> ac alia publica regni negotia, quae
                    privata nostra negotia intermittere nos compulserunt, non sunt passa nos rebus
                    nostris privatis invigilare, sed eas ad aliud tempus reiicere et relinquere
                    coegerunt, atque ideo ea saltem ratione hic <placeName>Viennae</placeName>
                    mansimus et ne suam maiestatem hac vice in itinere sequeremur. A sua maiestate
                    obtinuimus, ut iamtandem rebus quoque nostris privatis prospicere possemus, post
                    discessum itaque suae maiestatis censuram ipsam per tres fere dies laborando
                    diligenter revidimus ac nostram quoque moderationem secundum articulos
                    descripsissemus. Quam pro faciliori inventione <add corresp="scriba"
                        type="insert">secundum</add> capita articulorum cifris notatam unacum nostra
                    opinione ac moderatione similiter cifris notata, nec non duobus regestis super
                    inquisitione et rectificatione conscriptis per egregium <persName>Georgium
                        litteratum Katthyth</persName>,<note xml:id="note.2">The Croatian Kachich
                        family was famous around this time, see <hi rend="smallcap">Petrichevich
                            Horváth</hi> 1941, 226.</note> cuius opera in hac revisione usi sumus,
                    Dominationibus Vestris remisimus, si qua in re nos servitori <del
                        corresp="Olahus">nostros</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="corr">nostro</add>
                    indulsisse perspexerint, id non in aliam partem interpretari velint, nisi quod
                    in ea moderatione limites aequitatis transcendere noluimus, et quod rationem
                    etiam temporis ac loci, ubi <persName>Dobo</persName> officium exercuit,
                    habuimus. </p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">[2.] Quare Dominationes Vestras rogamus diligenter, velint,
                    quantocitius fieri poterit, nostram moderationem cognoscere atque haec negotia
                    primo quoque tempore expedire, ut interim, quoad maiestas regia ex <del
                        corresp="Olahus">Gracio</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="corr"
                            ><placeName>Grecio</placeName></add><note xml:id="note.3">Graz.</note>
                    rediens hic <placeName>Viennae</placeName> pausabit et se ad alias regiones <del
                        corresp="Olahus">non</del> movebit, totius negotii finis per nos atque
                    Dominationes Vestras imponi possit. Videtur autem ad inquisitionem eiusmodi
                    negotiorum pro parte camerae regiae maiestatis sufficiens esse <persName>Petrus
                        litteratus Gwtthensis</persName>,<note xml:id="note.4">Péter Gutai was
                        Counter-signer <hi rend="italic">(contrascriba)</hi> of Eger between
                        1549–1558, after which he became Royal Controller (1557–1563), see <hi
                            rend="smallcap">Kenyeres</hi> 2006, 60–61.</note> modernus in arce
                    Agriensi contrascriba regius, cui et nos ex nostris aliquem pro commodiori
                    inquisitione adiungemus. Scripsimus<note xml:id="note.5">We do not know this
                        letter.</note> etiam <persName>Stephano Dobo</persName>, ut rationes quoque
                    anni praesentis 1551 quamprimum conficere ac <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert"
                        >nobis vel</add> Dominationibus Vestris <milestone unit="pb"/>mittere curet,
                    ut eo citius totum rationis dandae negotium perfici possit. Cetera Dominationes
                    Vestrae fusius a praedicto <persName>Georgio litterato</persName> cognoscent per
                    quem Dominationibus Vestris seorsum et privatim, et communiter quoque
                    nuntiavimus. Quas optamus valere feliciter.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4"><placeName>Viennae</placeName> 23. die mensis Novembris 1551.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.5">[3.] <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Censuram Dominationum
                        Vestrarum cum nostra moderatione conferant faciantque unum corpus
                        responsionis ad rationes <persName>Dobonis</persName> dandae. Quae postea
                        illic tempore eo, quo videbitur fore commodius, mitti poterit, faciant
                        itaque Dominationes Vestrae me de voluntate earum quamprimum certiorem, ut
                        possim designare hominem aliquem meum idoneum ad inquisitionem similcum
                        contrascriba fidelem faciendam. Has licet litteras <del corresp="editor"
                            >licet</del> adscribi iusserim etiam <del corresp="Olahus">ad</del>
                        domino <persName>Nitriensi</persName>,<note xml:id="note.6">Ferenc
                            Thurzó.</note> arbitratus eum <placeName>Posonii</placeName> esse, sed
                        quia audio nondum eum rediisse <placeName>Posonium</placeName>, Dominationes
                        Vestrae velint sine eo negotio huic finem imponere rogo. Quae feliciter
                        valeant.</add></p>
                <p xml:id="p.6">
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Vester Agriensis etc. manu
                            propria.</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.7">Reverendis ac egregiis dominis Francisco Thwrzo de Bethlenffalwa,
                    episcopo Nittriensi praefecto ac ceteris consiliariis Hungaricae camerae regiae
                    maiestatis etc. dominis fratribus et amicis honorandis.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
